id: pm-5rge
title: Add integration test for background-refresh (instant mutations) non-blocking behavior
description: "The non-blocking background semantic refresh (PR #87, 2026-05-31) was the biggest perf win: create 2581->239ms, update 1693->265ms. The unit test in tests/unit/search-cache.spec.ts line 668 ('search background refresh') covers the cache-level behavior, but there is no integration test that verifies the end-to-end guarantee: a create/update command returns before the search reindex completes, and a subsequent search eventually reflects the change."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 3
tags[4]: "area:tests",background-refresh,performance,search
